Last updated: 29/09/2025
Thank you for playing Shape Shift Color Blast.
Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our mobile game.
1. Information We Collect
We do not collect personally identifiable information directly. However, third-party services integrated into the game may collect certain data:
AdMob (by Google)
Used to display ads. AdMob may collect advertising IDs, device information, and interaction data to provide personalized and non-personalized ads.
Learn more about Google‚Äôs Privacy Policy
Firebase (by Google)
Used for analytics, crash reports, and performance monitoring. Firebase may collect device identifiers, app usage data, and diagnostic information.
Learn more about Firebase Privacy & Security
2. How We Use the Information
The information collected via these services may be used to:
Display relevant ads (AdMob)
Understand how players use the game (Firebase Analytics)
Improve app stability and performance (Firebase Crashlytics & Performance)
Measure ad impressions and reward distribution (AdMob + Firebase events)
3. Third-Party Services
Our game uses third-party SDKs which may collect and process data under their own privacy policies:
Google AdMob
Google Firebase (Analytics, Crashlytics, Performance Monitoring)
We do not control these third parties. Please review their policies for more information.
4. Data Retention & Security
We do not store or share personal data on our own servers.
All data collection is handled by Google services (AdMob and Firebase).
We take reasonable measures to ensure your data is handled securely.
5. Children‚Äôs Privacy
Our game is designed for general audiences. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children under 13 (or under the age defined by local laws).
If you believe your child has provided personal data, please contact us so we can take steps to remove it.
6. Your Choices
You can disable personalized ads via your device settings:
On iOS: Settings ‚Üí Privacy ‚Üí Tracking / Advertising
On Android: Google Settings ‚Üí Ads ‚Üí Opt out of Ads Personalization
You can also uninstall the game at any time to stop all data collection.
7. Updates to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted within the app or on this page.
8. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, you can contact us at:
